title: A Stranger Apologized To My Husband For Being White
description: Whiteness is a sin these days and Kira Davis told a story on the Babylon Bee podcast about how a stranger apologized for being white — to her black husband.

title: Cancel Culture Is Coming For All Of Our Tweets
description: Kyle, Ethan, and Kira Davis discuss the damage 'Cancel Culture' is doing to everyone who has ever tweeted in their lifetime.
